{"type": "article", "id": 28534, "title": "极简座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-22T06:53:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702154944uxl3CmIztUw8i7ar.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>如果你喜欢坐在角落的安全感，北川大輔设计的这款 <a href=\"http://www.designforindustry.jp/works/corner\">Corner</a> 座椅会是一个不错的选择。Corner 向两个方向打开，呈 L 字型，可以同时感受到被包围的安全感和开阔的宽敞感。上方的坐垫带给人一种柔软舒适的印象，与下方纤细扁平的金属椅腿形成了鲜明对比。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154942BTKUoCXcRan52GYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154943wpU2JV9uXDcaY5ZC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154943AH1Pl9EaoYNJwR7x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702154944QZcuNG3lLBYDb5mM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}